keys.string: Having one on one time with the professors helped me to know them a lot better. I don’t have class the rest of the week, so the world is my oyster.
I have weird dream tonight. The voice of God comes to me and says “If you missed the item for the office hours today, you can’t go get it later.”
He keeps talking, “Also the game autosaves each scene so you’ll have to restart from the beginning.”
